      "message": "(unrelated, but I wonder what\u0027s the runtime overhead of this trick on happy path? is it as fast as just returning errors as usual? IIUC, KeyTok is a very hot functions and it might be better to copy-paste 20 lines of error checking code to speed it up even a bit)",
